{"article_id":"jVqn7dAYKvCAX7a9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"`` I underestimated how difficult it would be , ''","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Davis says","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"The filibuster of Texas Sen. Wendy Davis became a viral sensation","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"The White House took notice of her abortion rights stand","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Critics say","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"the bill would have shut most of the state 's abortion clinics","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"A day after a filibuster and a raucous crowd in the state Capitol foiled passage of a bill","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"that would have imposed strict new regulations on abortion in Texas ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Gov . Rick Perry vowed Wednesday to try again .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Perry said","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"the Legislature would convene July 1 in special session","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"to take up the abortion bill ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"which was declared dead before dawn Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"The bill failed after a night of drama in Austin","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"during which a lone lawmaker talked for more than 10 hours in an attempt","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"to run out the clock on a special session .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Chants of `` shame ! shame ! shame ! '' from spectators","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"who had filled the building","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"drowned out the efforts of Republican lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"as they tried to pass it minutes before midnight .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"`` We will not allow the breakdown of decorum and decency to prevent us from doing what the people of this state hired us to do , ''","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Perry said in a statement","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"calling lawmakers back into another special session .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Texans `` value life","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and want to protect women and the unborn , ''","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Perry 's announcement came","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"a day before he was to address the National Right to Life convention in Dallas on Thursday .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"And it came on a day","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"when abortion rights advocates found a new hero in state","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Sen. Wendy Davis , D-Fort Worth .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Though Republicans control the state Senate ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Davis tried to block the abortion bill","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"by attempting a 13-hour filibuster Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Perry :","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Filibuster senator was a teen mom","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"MUST WATCH Perry :","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Filibuster senator was a teen mom 01:53","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"Watch how Texas Senate filibuster began","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Watch how Texas Senate filibuster began","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"00:45","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Texas House debates , passes abortion bill","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Texas House debates , passes abortion bill 01:37","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"`` I underestimated how difficult it would be","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"-- both physically and mentally , ''","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Davis told CNN 's `` AC360 '' on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"`` About two hours in , I realized","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"I was in for a long day .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"My back started hurting pretty early on","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"and began to really hurt","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"as the hours ticked by . ''","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"But ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"the energy from the packed gallery `` kept me going throughout the day . ''","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Davis fell short of her goal by less than three hours","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"when the chair ruled","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"she had gone off topic .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"The gallery erupted in boos .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Her fellow Democrats stalled for time with procedural tactics .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"And","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"as the clock wound down ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"opponents of the bill drowned out proceedings on the floor ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"preventing lawmakers from completing a vote in time","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"to get it passed .","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"At 3 a.m. , Lt. Gov . David Dewhurst stepped to the Senate floor","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"to declare the bill dead","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"and the special session over .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"`` We empowered the voice of people in Texas and people","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"who wanted to stand against this intrusion , this big government intrusion , into their personal lives , ''","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Davis said Wednesday night .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Even if the bill winds up passing in the next special session ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"the reaction will not be split along partisan lines ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"she predicted .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"`` It 's a reaction","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"coming from Republicans , independents and Democrats alike ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"which is saying :","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Governor Perry , Lieutenant Governor Dewhurst , stay out of my private decision-making . ''","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"The bill would have banned most abortions after 20 weeks of pregnancy","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"and tightened standards on abortion clinics and the doctors","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"who work at them .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Critics said","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"the measure would have shut most of the abortion clinics in Texas .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"`` He","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"( Perry )","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"lost this fight in regular session ,","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"even after they broke the rules","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"he and his allies lost again in front of the entire country last night , ''","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"said Cecile Richards , president of the Planned Parenthood Action Fund , in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"`` They tried every trick in the book ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"blocking testimony from the very women","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"whose lives would be affected ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"voting in the middle of the night ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"shutting down the debate","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"-","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"they could n't get this done","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"because Texans would not let them . ''","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"Wearing pink sneakers ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"Davis , 50 , took to the floor of the chamber late Tuesday morning","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"to criticize the bill .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Rules called for her to stand , unaided , until midnight ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"for the filibuster to succeed .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"She was not allowed to sit down , lean or take a bathroom break ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"and she was allowed three warnings","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"before the Senate was to be allowed to vote on whether to stop the filibuster .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"The senator spent much of the time","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"reading testimony and messages from women","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"decrying the bill","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"and recounting the struggles","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"they , their friends or relatives faced","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"before birth control and abortion were legalized .","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"`` Women realize","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"that these bills will not protect their health , ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"`` They will only reduce their access to abortion providers","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"and limit their ability","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"to make their own family-planning decisions . ''","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"Early in the diatribe , her comments were ruled off topic","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"and she was given her first warning .","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"During the evening , a fellow senator helped Davis put on a back brace ,","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"which was ruled to have violated filibuster rules ,","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"and she got her second warning .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"Finally , at about 10 p.m. , Davis talked about the abortion pill , RU486 ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"and the chairman ruled again","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"that her comments were off topic .","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"But a member of the Senate then moved","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"that the ruling be appealed ,","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"and its status was in doubt .","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"The final hours of the session were marked by confusing parliamentary maneuvers","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"until Sen. Leticia Van de Putte stepped to the microphone ,","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"ending the debate .","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"`` At what point must a female senator raise her hand or her voice","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"to be recognized over the male colleagues in the room ? ''","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"the Democratic senator asked","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"after she had been ignored .","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"At 15 minutes before midnight , the gallery erupted in applause and chants of `` Wendy ! Wendy ! Wendy ! ''","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"As the session ended ,","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"Davis waded into the crowd of supporters","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"and praised them as `` the people","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"who truly made this happen . ''","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"Texas Right to Life blamed `` the angry mob of protesters in the Senate gallery '' for the failure of the bill","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"to pass .","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"`` Ultimately , we should be encouraged","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"that we had the votes","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"and that so many came to support the bill , ''","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"the anti-abortion group said on its website .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"`` We will continue to work","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"to pass Pro-Life legislation","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"that protects women","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"and saves lives in Texas . ''","depth":14},{"id":159,"text":"Davis ' stand captivated abortion rights advocates from coast to coast ,","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"prompting the hashtag # standwithwendy on Twitter","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"`` Something special is happening in Austin tonight , ''","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"said a post on President Barack Obama 's official Twitter account .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"The account is run by Organizing for Action , a nonprofit group","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"established","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"to support the president 's legislative agenda .","depth":13},{"id":166,"text":"`` Whatever the outcome , @ WendyDavisTexas efforts entered her into the pantheon of American heroes tonight . ''","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"Heady times for Davis ,","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"who was first elected to the Texas Senate in 2008 ,","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"defeating a longtime Republican incumbent","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"to do so .","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"Last year , she staged a filibuster","depth":5},{"id":172,"text":"to force a special session in an attempt","depth":6},{"id":173,"text":"to stop $ 5 billion in cuts to Texas public schools ,","depth":6},{"id":174,"text":"according to her website","depth":4},{"id":175,"text":"Davis ,","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"who became a single mother at age 19 ,","depth":6},{"id":177,"text":"went on to graduate with honors from Harvard Law School ,","depth":5},{"id":178,"text":"it says .","depth":4},{"id":179,"text":"Her filibuster was no record .","depth":4},{"id":180,"text":"In 1977 , Sen. Bill Meier staged a 43-hour marathon .","depth":4},{"id":181,"text":"The special session ends with irony ,","depth":4},{"id":182,"text":"Twitter user Cody Beckner said ,","depth":5},{"id":183,"text":"echoing the governor 's own words .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":367,"left":354,"right":366,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":354,"left":190,"right":353,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":190,"left":0,"right":189,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":189,"left":186,"right":188,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":186,"left":185,"right":3,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":4,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":353,"left":217,"right":352,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":209,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":196,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":192,"right":195,"relation":"elaboration","nuc